node.text:
Struggling with writer's block, a novelist finds inspiration when she meets a down-on-his-luck oddball who constantly changes personas and alter egos to cope with the past and avoid reality.

With: @ilizasheslinger @davidkoechner @cleopatracoleman @trezzo_ @nickthune #ad #therightonemovie

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by self care ✨ life hacks on September 01, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'just cancelled plans and when they asked why I said "honestly, I don't want to go" and WOW. HOW POWERFUL.I'm used to giving bullshit excuses or just not showing up (aka being a flake) and WOW actually taking my power back having autonomy over my life is liberating AF'.

Photo by self care ✨ life hacks on September 01, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Rowann @InndoClassics PSA: your friend goes ΜΙΑ for awhile or starts to seem distant, stop confronting them with negativity! Like they're being shady or something Call em up& ask if everything is okay. invite em to lunch, pray for em!| mean you never know what someone is going through..be blessed'.

Photo by self care ✨ life hacks on September 01, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Snow Black Cindy @Ebony_QT "Stop choosing length over health" This applies to friendships, relationships, and hair. Let it go. A concept.'.
